description: Full Planning Application for the construction of 5 buildings of between 5 - 8 storeys in height, with associated basement, comprising up to 189 residential units and provision of new office (B1a) and leisure (D2) floorspace and a new publicly accessible caf (A3). Associated car and cycle parking, refuse storage and amenity space (SUBJECT TO DEED OF VARIATION DATED 20 NOVEMBER 2020)
